high_descs: go to counter to the right of refrigerator with potato
pick up knife to the left of potato from counter
turn left, go to counter with yellow apple to the left of white cupboard
slice tomato behind yellow apple on counter
turn around, go to microwave on the counter to the right
place knife in microwave, close microwave
turn around, go to counter with apple and sliced tomato to the right
pick up tomato slice behind apple from counter
go to sink to the left
place tomato slice in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up tomato slice from sink
turn around, go to microwave to the right
place tomato slice to the left of potato in microwave, close microwave
anns.task_desc: place knife and washed tomato slice in microwave

high_descs: Go forward to the stove top, go to the left to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn left, go forward to the counter with the apple and tomato.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Turn around, go forward to the stove top, turn right, go forward to the wall, turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn left, go forward to the stove top, turn left, go forward to the counter with the apple and the tomato.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn left, go to the right side of the sink, face the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink, take the tomato slice from the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the stove top, turn right, go forward to the wall, turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Walk around the room to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Walk around the room to face the sliced tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink and then remove it.
Walk around the room to face the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To clean a slice of tomato plus store it in the microwave.
